	<a class="citerefentry" href="glTranslate.xml"><span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glTranslate</span></span></a>
	</p></div><div class="refsect1" title="Copyright"><a id="copyright"></a><h2>Copyright</h2><p>
